data.description: All financing available, unit #2 in our building just received an FHA spot approval. Conventional or Assumable $394,800 VA loan at 3.1% for a veteran only. Seller wants to keep his entitlement. Loan is at apx 3.1% with an apx balance of ,394,800. 3-Bedroom 2 Bath, private rear patio with two assigned parking spots all within the private gated community. Ground Level location, tranquil Four-Unit building situated for ultimate convenience, this property offers easy access to freeways leading in all directions. Your commute has never been easier! Step into a home that feels brand new! The bathrooms have been thoughtfully cared for, tub-shower combination in both baths. The kitchen features sleek cabinets and  stainless steel appliances. A rear patio beckons for BBQs and outdoor relaxation. It's the perfect spot to unwind and entertain while  creating lasting memories with friends and family. Well-maintained gated grounds at the end of a cul-de-sac, You'll appreciate the sense of security and community that comes with it. Everywhere you look, you'll see evidence of the pride of ownership that permeates this community. Well-kept grounds and common areas enhance your living experience. Enjoy the convenience of on-site laundry rooms, two assigned parking spots, play lot with a picnic table and seating.
